class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ne_of_apply_ne</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Even</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">norm_num</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
